Senhoras e senhores,

00:18:23.494 --> 00:18:25.352
os membros da equipa de investigação,

00:18:25.352 --> 00:18:29.353
Elliott Rouse e Nathan Villagaray-Carski.

00:18:29.776 --> 00:18:32.187
Elliott e Nathan.

